    "We find an average pairwise agreement of 71.36% for Intentionality, 70.70% for Motivation, 85.21% for Self-Efficacy, and 81.09% for Self-Regulation.",
    "We use text-davinci-003 for all of our GPT-3 models.",
    "For Agency measurement models (Section 7), we sample the highest probable next tokens by setting the temperature value to 0 (determinstic sampling).",
    "For dialogue generation models (Section 8), we use top-p sampling with p = 0.6.",
    "For in-context learning methods, we experimented with k = 5, 10, 15, and 20 and found k = 10 to be the most effective based on a qualitative assessment of 10 examples."
